    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035970/extras/e9ca5a71e0386e69cb464eeff54150f3.avif?t=1719071844\" width=601 height=73 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035970/extras/72709abe8af7d6cde397fbec6e9034e5.poster.avif?t=1719071844\" width=606 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035970/extras/72709abe8af7d6cde397fbec6e9034e5.webm?t=1719071844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035970/extras/72709abe8af7d6cde397fbec6e9034e5.mp4?t=1719071844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Discover the French mountains in style on skis!</strong><br>Carve your way through the powder, weave between trees, soar over rocks, and cross rivers. Pull off tricks, skid, and jump, but most importantly, avoid crashing!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035970/extras/a56867af3bbf08633b62c6045b9e1374.webp?t=1719071844\" width=600 height=34 /></span><br>Explore the French mountains or race against the clock! Each mountain has several trails, so it's up to you to find the one that suits you best, whether you're a nature lover or a speed freak!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035970/extras/af9009b87493ea76d730e894314ee5b8.poster.avif?t=1719071844\" width=606 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035970/extras/af9009b87493ea76d730e894314ee5b8.webm?t=1719071844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035970/extras/af9009b87493ea76d730e894314ee5b8.mp4?t=1719071844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035970/extras/eb0a341d12c99ce1b035994303557e03.webp?t=1719071844\" width=600 height=34 /></span><br>It all depends on your approach! You can follow the main path or use your sense of observation and creativity to get there as quickly as possible!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035970/extras/8c6cdf2917b8ce35059fc8579a47460e.poster.avif?t=1719071844\" width=606 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035970/extras/8c6cdf2917b8ce35059fc8579a47460e.webm?t=1719071844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035970/extras/8c6cdf2917b8ce35059fc8579a47460e.mp4?t=1719071844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
